WEBVTT

1
00:02:32.279 --> 00:02:36.118
My dear father. My brave father.

2
00:02:37.479 --> 00:02:40.638
You once said people are mortal.

3
00:02:40.839 --> 00:02:44.518
My breaths are numbered now.

4
00:02:45.159 --> 00:02:48.358
I worked truly hard.

5
00:02:48.639 --> 00:02:54.078
To take your inheritance
and gift forward.

6
00:02:54.959 --> 00:03:00.918
We own many castles and realms.

7
00:03:01.759 --> 00:03:05.518
Your armies are at
the gates of Bursa.

8
00:03:05.919 --> 00:03:09.278
The city is about to fall.

9
00:03:10.119 --> 00:03:14.998
The sacred fire you
started will be the hope...

10
00:03:15.399 --> 00:03:19.198
of the Islam world
for centuries. InshaAllah.

11
00:03:27.239 --> 00:03:30.278
Selamun aleykum. Osman Bey.

12
00:03:31.759 --> 00:03:33.478
Aleykum selam.

13
00:03:33.679 --> 00:03:37.078
-May your day be blessed.
-Be my guest.

14
00:03:43.839 --> 00:03:48.278
-It's time. huh?
-Brave man. Osman Bey.

15
00:03:49.559 --> 00:03:54.518
Your father spread the seeds of the
state and you grew it into a sapling.

16
00:03:54.679 --> 00:04:00.118
Orhan Bey. InshaAllah. will turn
the sapling into a great plane tree.

17
00:04:00.799 --> 00:04:03.398
Orhan. the apple of my eyes.

18
00:04:03.919 --> 00:04:07.958
The wise men say that
a son is a father's secret.

19
00:04:08.239 --> 00:04:14.798
We ask you. Osman Bey. to point out who
the new bey will be while you are alive.

20
00:04:15.279 --> 00:04:18.477
Kill the fire of unrest
before it even starts.

21
00:04:18.598 --> 00:04:25.837
Otherwise. the last hope of the Islam
world and the Turkic world might be wasted.

22
00:04:26.078 --> 00:04:31.317
If Kayi! people have to deal with
the unrest. hypocrisy and betrayal.

23
00:04:31.518 --> 00:04:33.957
we can't stand this.

24
00:04:34.478 --> 00:04:39.997
We ask you to give Orhan
Bey the seal of beylic.

25
00:06:04.758 --> 00:06:07.397
Flavius

26
00:06:07.758 --> 00:06:12.997
Before you even take a step. Orhan
Bey knows what steps you will take.

27
00:06:13.438 --> 00:06:16.277
He also knew you
were coming here.

28
00:06:16.478 --> 00:06:19.797
We will bury you
inside that tunnel now.

29
00:08:08.558 --> 00:08:12.157
Just keep running.

30
00:09:00.957 --> 00:09:04.556
My Osman.

31
00:09:07.317 --> 00:09:15.076
When this chair. which swallows whoever can't carry
the burden of thousand-year-old dream became my fate.

32
00:09:15.277 --> 00:09:17.636
my challenge started. Malhun.

33
00:09:18.317 --> 00:09:23.356
I thought the hardest
part was carrying it.

34
00:09:25.077 --> 00:09:27.676
You carried without
even stumbling.

35
00:09:27.957 --> 00:09:30.476
And you will keep carrying.

36
00:09:31.157 --> 00:09:33.556
And it has turned out that...

37
00:09:33.637 --> 00:09:37.836
my biggest challenge is to
choose who deserves the chair.

38
00:09:51.037 --> 00:09:56.636
All those dreams and what
happened were because of this.

39
00:09:57.397 --> 00:10:02.076
However. it's time.

40
00:10:03.757 --> 00:10:06.276
I'm assembling
the council today.

41
00:10:06.717 --> 00:10:11.796
I'm handing over the
chair to the new owner.

42
00:10:19.797 --> 00:10:21.596
I swear..

43
00:10:21.837 --> 00:10:27.836
I swear Orhan won't reach any of
his goals as long as I keep breathing.

44
00:10:28.317 --> 00:10:30.276
I swear. Didar.

45
00:10:30.557 --> 00:10:35.396
He insulted my
duty. army and beylic!

46
00:10:35.397 --> 00:10:37.756
I will insult him!

47
00:10:38.357 --> 00:10:40.276
What about Alaeddin?

48
00:10:40.437 --> 00:10:44.316
He accepted being his brother s
shadow and betrayed me.

49
00:10:44.517 --> 00:10:46.356
I will show no
mercy for him either!

50
00:10:46.637 --> 00:10:49.676
You will see what
I'm going to do. Didar!

51
00:10:49.997 --> 00:10:52.676
I won't let them
waste the state!

52
00:10:52.957 --> 00:10:55.396
Never!

53
00:10:56.277 --> 00:10:58.956
Do I have permission. my Bey?

54
00:11:00.117 --> 00:11:02.396
Come in.

55
00:11:03.677 --> 00:11:05.916
Father.

56
00:11:07.077 --> 00:11:10.276
Alaeddin Bey
wants to talk to you.

57
00:11:15.037 --> 00:11:18.916
Come in. Alaeddin Bey.

58
00:11:21.837 --> 00:11:24.716
Selamun aleykum.

59
00:11:25.357 --> 00:11:28.076
Aleykum selam.

60
00:11:28.397 --> 00:11:30.796
Sahinshah Bey

61
00:11:31.437 --> 00:11:36.596
I am here to tell you that no matter
what happens. you are an uncle to me.

62
00:11:38.677 --> 00:11:42.516
There is no need for such
destruction. right. Sahinshah Bey?

63
00:11:42.637 --> 00:11:46.516
I am not the one who
destroys. Alaeddin Bey.

64
00:11:46.837 --> 00:11:50.836
You were the one who
destroyed me before my Alps.

65
00:11:52.477 --> 00:11:55.676
You were more than a
nephew to me. you were my son.

66
00:11:57.437 --> 00:12:01.556
I did what I had to
do. I would do it again

67
00:12:01.877 --> 00:12:05.076
But I know you understand me.

68
00:12:05.237 --> 00:12:07.076
I understand you.

69
00:12:07.237 --> 00:12:09.716
I have always understood you.

70
00:12:09.957 --> 00:12:13.196
I thought you d
understand me as well...

71
00:12:13.717 --> 00:12:17.156
but you let me down.

72
00:12:18.077 --> 00:12:20.156
Father...

73
00:12:20.277 --> 00:12:25.116
Even if the paths are parted.
don't we all share the same dream?

74
00:12:26.957 --> 00:12:29.796
Dont...

75
00:12:33.117 --> 00:12:35.396
Osman Bey is
gathering the council!

76
00:12:35.557 --> 00:12:39.116
He is waiting for all
the Beys In his tent!

77
00:12:39.917 --> 00:12:43.036
Did you know about this council?

78
00:12:43.757 --> 00:12:47.156
We'll find out when we go there.

79
00:12:52.117 --> 00:12:54.315
Sahinshah Bey.

80
00:12:54.476 --> 00:12:57.355
I want you to leave
this resentment aside...

81
00:12:57.676 --> 00:13:01.115
and stand by our
side like you always do.

82
00:13:01.276 --> 00:13:04.595
Sahinshah Bey...

83
00:13:06.436 --> 00:13:09.955
EyvAllah now.

84
00:13:31.916 --> 00:13:35.235
Hay MashaAllah.

85
00:13:38.916 --> 00:13:41.115
You want to become Alps. huh?

86
00:13:41.676 --> 00:13:45.275
First. you n ed to learn how
to fight without your swords.

87
00:13:45.636 --> 00:13:48.315
Bravery is fighting
alone against twenty men.

88
00:13:48.356 --> 00:13:52.475
An Alp's fist becomes a sword
and his foot becomes a spear.

89
00:13:52.516 --> 00:13:56.195
An Alp proves himself not in
hard times. but in impossible ones.

90
00:13:56.356 --> 00:13:58.395
What are you waiting for?

91
00:13:58.596 --> 00:14:00.715
Let's see if you deserve it.

92
00:14:01.076 --> 00:14:04.195
Come on. attack!

93
00:14:39.076 --> 00:14:42.515
In war. victory does not come
from having many soldiers.

94
00:14:42.596 --> 00:14:45.355
In war. victory
comes from the heart!

95
00:15:16.236 --> 00:15:17.915
We are close.

96
00:15:18.196 --> 00:15:20.795
We will train hard.
but we are close.

97
00:15:20.876 --> 00:15:24.515
Those who do not train enough
will find themselves in a grave soon.

98
00:15:37.116 --> 00:15:40.075
Selamun aleykum. -Aleykum selam.

99
00:15:40.156 --> 00:15:42.635
I brought news from Orhan
Bey. AbdurRahman Alp.

100
00:15:42.796 --> 00:15:45.915
Here.

101
00:15:57.676 --> 00:16:00.515
Kayi's brave men...

102
00:16:01.356 --> 00:16:04.875
What would you say if I told you
the path of war is ahead of us?

103
00:16:04.916 --> 00:16:09.275
We are either
martyrs or veterans!

104
00:16:09.476 --> 00:16:12.995
Orhan Bey ordered
us to conquer Yarhisar.

105
00:16:13.116 --> 00:16:16.155
War is bairam. war
is celebration for us!

106
00:16:16.316 --> 00:16:20.555
-Will you fight with us?
-We will!

107
00:16:20.996 --> 00:16:24.555
Then dark steel
will shed dark blood!

108
00:16:24.636 --> 00:16:27.075
Kayis will take what
belongs to Kayis!

109
00:16:27.156 --> 00:16:32.995
Allah is the Greatest!

110
00:16:43.756 --> 00:16:46.035
Since when do you
have these symptoms?

111
00:16:46.116 --> 00:16:49.915
It's new... very new.

112
00:16:52.756 --> 00:16:55.315
What is wrong with me?

113
00:16:55.556 --> 00:16:56.915
Why are you silent?

114
00:16:56.996 --> 00:17:00.795
Wait. my daughter.
Calm down.

115
00:17:08.076 --> 00:17:13.754
What is wrong with
me? Tell me. Sadi Kadin.

116
00:17:47.315 --> 00:17:49.474
Ya Ilahe...

117
00:17:50.635 --> 00:17:58.234
You are the Owner of the seven floors of
ground. the seven floors of sky. and all realms.

118
00:17:59.195 --> 00:18:03.234
You are the One Who
opens the conquest of hearts.

119
00:18:04.275 --> 00:18:12.674
These soldiers. these brave Alps. are entrusted
to loyal servants that seek Your pleasure.

120
00:18:13.475 --> 00:18:17.394
O. my Allah. Who gives
the love of battle to hearts.

121
00:18:17.995 --> 00:18:22.794
Make their swords sharp
and their intentions pure.

122
00:18:22.915 --> 00:18:27.954
Cover the heavens
over them like armor.

123
00:18:28.955 --> 00:18:31.674
Every conquest comes from You.

124
00:18:32.195 --> 00:18:35.034
Every conquest leads to You.

125
00:18:36.355 --> 00:18:42.594
Walk with them. so
they may walk with You.

126
00:18:42.755 --> 00:18:46.514
May You grant them victory.

127
00:18:46.755 --> 00:18:49.354
Aameen.

128
00:19:20.395 --> 00:19:23.954
My Bey.. Where have you been?
I've been looking for you everywhere.

129
00:19:23.995 --> 00:19:26.074
What happened this time. Halil?

130
00:19:26.315 --> 00:19:30.394
Osman Bey has gathered the
council. Everyone is waiting for you.

131
00:19:31.995 --> 00:19:36.194
May it be good. I heard that Osman Bey
Is going to make an important decision.

132
00:19:36.515 --> 00:19:39.034
But I don't know
what it is about.

133
00:19:50.635 --> 00:19:52.714
The enemy is at our door.

134
00:19:53.075 --> 00:19:54.594
Bursa lies in wait.

135
00:19:55.075 --> 00:20:00.034
And we keep meeting here instead of
fighting against the enemy at the front.

136
00:20:00.395 --> 00:20:02.634
We keep bothering our Osman Bey.

137
00:20:02.755 --> 00:20:06.034
We make him repeat his
words over and over again.

138
00:20:06.235 --> 00:20:07.994
While we are
wasting time here...

139
00:20:08.195 --> 00:20:11.754
many Yarhisars will fall.

140
00:20:15.835 --> 00:20:17.034
Selamun aleykum.

141
00:20:17.115 --> 00:20:20.634
Ve aleykum selam.

142
00:20:26.515 --> 00:20:28.314
Thanks to Allah.

143
00:20:28.395 --> 00:20:32.994
This time you've made it to the council
before Osman Bey arrives. Orhan Bey.

144
00:20:38.235 --> 00:20:41.474
Attention! Osman Bey!

145
00:20:53.995 --> 00:20:57.794
-Selamun aleykum.
-Ve aleykum selam.

146
00:20:58.235 --> 00:21:01.394
You may sit.

147
00:21:06.835 --> 00:21:17.754
With Almighty Allah's 99 names. Who says "Be".
and it is. and fills our heart with faith...

148
00:21:17.835 --> 00:21:20.994
I am starting our council.

149
00:21:22.355 --> 00:21:24.674
What i1s the
situation in Yarhisar?

150
00:21:25.155 --> 00:21:26.354
Tell me.

151
00:21:26.435 --> 00:21:32.793
Yarhisar being in the hands of the enemies
cast a dark shadow over our council.

152
00:21:33.034 --> 00:21:35.753
Don't worry. Avci Bey.

153
00:21:35.874 --> 00:21:39.553
That dark shadow is
now over Temurtas.

154
00:21:39.674 --> 00:21:44.273
He will understand that
Kayi is not like other Beylics.

155
00:21:45.514 --> 00:21:50.993
When has Kayi ever given up on taking
its revenge that it would give up now?

156
00:21:51.194 --> 00:21:56.713
If we are here today. it's
because we know when to attack.

157
00:21:59.314 --> 00:22:01.233
Sahinshah Bey.

158
00:22:01.394 --> 00:22:05.713
You get excited with every
conquest and excite all of us.

159
00:22:05.834 --> 00:22:08.553
You are very quiet now.

160
00:22:09.354 --> 00:22:15.073
The excitement inside me is prevented
by our martyrs in Yarhisar. my Bey.

161
00:22:15.194 --> 00:22:17.553
I know your heart burns too.

162
00:22:17.754 --> 00:22:21.353
I am asking if thereis a
Bey who can put out this fire.

163
00:22:21.474 --> 00:22:23.913
There is.

164
00:22:25.274 --> 00:22:27.793
In Kayi. we will always
have soldiers and Beys.

165
00:22:27.874 --> 00:22:34.673
Don't you know that we will not leave Yarhisar. taken by
my father. to that treacherous Temurtas Sahinshah Bey?

166
00:22:36.314 --> 00:22:42.313
InshaAllah. this time you will
not act on your own. Orhan Bey.

167
00:22:42.434 --> 00:22:49.393
Since you don't want
Orhan Bey to act on his own...

168
00:22:49.674 --> 00:22:56.473
then we will follow
his word from now on.

169
00:23:05.314 --> 00:23:08.033
What do you mean. my Bey?

170
00:23:08.634 --> 00:23:13.033
I am chasing a dream.

171
00:23:13.314 --> 00:23:19.113
I see the plane tree rising
from my chest as my RedApple.

172
00:23:19.194 --> 00:23:26.113
I have shed many tears. I shed the
blood of my enemies without getting tired.

173
00:23:26.394 --> 00:23:33.473
I remembered the words of
our glorious Prophet (PBUH)..

174
00:23:33.834 --> 00:23:39.273
The prosperity of the world
lies on the back of a horse.

175
00:23:39.674 --> 00:23:44.553
That's why I did not
give up on this way

176
00:23:45.074 --> 00:23:48.513
My Beys. the
elderly of my tribe...

177
00:23:48.914 --> 00:23:53.073
Those who do not have
dreams cannot have a future.

178
00:23:53.434 --> 00:23:59.073
I have seen that the one who
sees my dream as his own...

179
00:23:59.314 --> 00:24:02.433
who cares for his
land instead of the chair...

180
00:24:02.714 --> 00:24:05.993
Is Orhan Bey.

181
00:24:14.634 --> 00:24:17.193
For this reason.

182
00:24:18.514 --> 00:24:21.193
Orhan Bey.

183
00:24:21.794 --> 00:24:28.233
now you are granted the
seal of my father Ertugrul Ghaz.

184
00:24:38.874 --> 00:24:41.033
Thanks to Allah. you are live.

185
00:24:41.434 --> 00:24:43.993
While you are leading
us. we don't need a regent.

186
00:24:44.234 --> 00:24:47.313
It is not regency son.

187
00:24:47.794 --> 00:24:54.313
It is the handover of the beylic and
the throne from me to my son Orhan.

188
00:25:03.234 --> 00:25:06.793
People are born to die.

189
00:25:07.034 --> 00:25:11.273
A Bey should know
how to abdicate...

190
00:25:11.594 --> 00:25:14.953
just like he
sits on the chair.

191
00:25:16.234 --> 00:25:18.233
Hear me.

192
00:25:18.514 --> 00:25:25.433
Orhan Bey is now
what I have been so far.

193
00:25:35.074 --> 00:25:40.033
Osman Bey. the greatest of
the great and the mighty ghazi.

194
00:25:40.314 --> 00:25:42.833
I'd die for you.

195
00:25:43.234 --> 00:25:46.872
I'd stop wherever
you tell me to stop.

196
00:25:48.633 --> 00:25:55.552
However. I don't want this chair
like this under these circumstances.

197
00:26:00.313 --> 00:26:03.672
-What are you saying. Orhan Bey?
-I'm saying...

198
00:26:04.113 --> 00:26:07.952
If all the beys don't
pledge loyalty to me here

199
00:26:08.273 --> 00:26:10.432
I won't want this beylic.

200
00:26:10.953 --> 00:26:13.632
There should be
no struggle of power.

201
00:26:13.793 --> 00:26:15.632
Now tell me.

202
00:26:15.873 --> 00:26:21.312
Is there anyone who
doesn't want me to the bey?

203
00:26:32.753 --> 00:26:35.432
Is there?

204
00:26:35.953 --> 00:26:37.912
There isn't. Orhan Bey.

205
00:26:38.113 --> 00:26:40.712
-There isn't. my Bey.
-There isn't.

206
00:26:40.913 --> 00:26:43.632
-There isn't.
-There isn't. my Bey.

207
00:26:43.873 --> 00:26:46.392
There isn't my Bey!

208
00:26:47.433 --> 00:26:51.192
You're talking like
Brunet Osman. Orhan Bey.

209
00:26:52.353 --> 00:26:57.432
Struggle of power would
collapse the chair. You're right.

210
00:26:58.713 --> 00:27:02.992
And receive what you deserve.

211
00:27:32.633 --> 00:27:38.352
This sword. handed over from my ancestor Suleyman
Shah to my grandfather Ertugrul and from him to you.

212
00:27:38.553 --> 00:27:39.992
IS NOW mine.

213
00:27:40.153 --> 00:27:42.912
I will hold this gift more
important than my life...

214
00:27:42.913 --> 00:27:47.352
and protect it for the peace and
the order of Kayi and all Oghuz people.

215
00:27:48.593 --> 00:27:50.392
For the record.

216
00:27:50.553 --> 00:27:55.232
As long as I keep this sword. we
will spend no days without conquest.

217
00:27:55.833 --> 00:27:58.112
May Allah help me.

218
00:27:58.353 --> 00:28:02.112
My beylic shall prosper
with you and prevail.

219
00:28:02.393 --> 00:28:04.952
-Aameen.
-Aameen.

220
00:28:05.473 --> 00:28:07.152
-Aameen.
-Aameen.

221
00:28:07.433 --> 00:28:11.952
Now you have the authority for
the hunt and assembling the council.

222
00:28:17.033 --> 00:28:18.672
As you command. my Bey.

223
00:28:18.913 --> 00:28:23.032
You have the command
now. Orhan Bey

224
00:29:00.753 --> 00:29:03.912
May your beylic be
blessed. Orhan Bey.

225
00:29:06.073 --> 00:29:09.032
Thank you. brother.

226
00:29:19.713 --> 00:29:25.032
May your kin prosper and grow bigger.
May your beylic be blessed. Orhan Bey.

227
00:29:27.273 --> 00:29:29.792
Thank you.

228
00:29:34.873 --> 00:29:38.152
You have the
command and the order.

229
00:29:38.393 --> 00:29:41.592
May Allah make it mubarak.

230
00:29:43.073 --> 00:29:45.632
Thanks

231
00:30:18.472 --> 00:30:21.831
May your beylic be
blessed. Orhan Bey.

232
00:31:08.232 --> 00:31:11.191
May it be blessed. my Bey.

233
00:31:12.952 --> 00:31:17.071
Thank you

234
00:31:20.632 --> 00:31:24.631
May it be blessed. my Bey.

235
00:31:28.912 --> 00:31:32.911
-May it be blessed. my Bey.
-Thank you.

236
00:31:36.232 --> 00:31:39.391
Oh my dear...

237
00:31:39.872 --> 00:31:42.911
Let me check your foot.

238
00:31:43.952 --> 00:31:47.111
It's better now thanks
to you Fatma Hatun.

239
00:31:47.712 --> 00:31:49.351
Fatma Hatun.

240
00:31:49.712 --> 00:31:52.231
Esma. take this.

241
00:31:56.552 --> 00:31:58.671
Yes. Yigit Bey?

242
00:31:59.312 --> 00:32:04.911
You are the heal of this tribe Fatma
Hatun. You cure everyone's wounds.

243
00:32:07.192 --> 00:32:10.391
-Astaghfirullah.
-You do. You do.

244
00:32:10.752 --> 00:32:13.231
I'm fine thanks to you.

245
00:32:15.552 --> 00:32:20.071
And I have been
waiting to talk to you.

246
00:32:21.752 --> 00:32:23.991
This is not a good
time. Yigit Bey.

247
00:32:24.192 --> 00:32:26.991
When is the good
time. Fatma Hatun?

248
00:32:27.632 --> 00:32:30.111
Something comes up every time.

249
00:32:30.472 --> 00:32:32.871
Words stick in my throat.

250
00:32:33.072 --> 00:32:35.671
And I can t talk to you.

251
00:32:36.432 --> 00:32:40.711
I want to give you a gift.

252
00:32:45.952 --> 00:32:48.711
What's that supposed
to mean. Yigit Bey?

253
00:32:50.632 --> 00:32:53.871
This is my gratitude for you.

254
00:32:54.112 --> 00:32:56.831
You saved my life.

255
00:32:57.072 --> 00:32:58.991
I owe you.

256
00:32:59.352 --> 00:33:02.551
A man should pay
his debt. I can t forget.

257
00:33:02.952 --> 00:33:06.831
I made it myself. For you.

258
00:33:11.552 --> 00:33:15.671
I didn't save you from death
to make you feel indebted.

259
00:33:16.632 --> 00:33:19.391
0 People of Kay!

260
00:33:19.592 --> 00:33:24.951
From now on. Orhan Bey
will sit on the chair of Kayi!

261
00:33:25.872 --> 00:33:29.311
For everyone's information!

262
00:33:38.832 --> 00:33:40.591
O people!

263
00:33:40.832 --> 00:33:43.231
For everyone's information!

264
00:33:43.512 --> 00:33:48.871
Halime. From now on. Orhan Bey
will sit on the chair of Kayi!

265
00:33:50.832 --> 00:33:53.871
May it be blessed for all of us.

266
00:33:54.472 --> 00:33:57.631
Finally. I knew it.

267
00:34:01.472 --> 00:34:04.791
Orhan Bey will be
worthy of his position.

268
00:34:05.392 --> 00:34:08.751
May it be mubarak for all of us

269
00:34:09.632 --> 00:34:14.551
I thought Osman Bey
would rule for longer

270
00:34:14.792 --> 00:34:19.910
Osman Bey is who he is because he doesn't
make decisions according to expectations.

271
00:34:23.191 --> 00:34:26.190
Malhun Hatun. you
don't seem surprised.

272
00:34:26.391 --> 00:34:30.190
Did you know before?
Why are you so curious. Didar?

273
00:34:30.471 --> 00:34:34.230
Do you have something to say
against Osman Bey's decision?

274
00:34:34.951 --> 00:34:37.230
Estaghfirullah.

275
00:34:37.591 --> 00:34:41.510
May 1t be blessed. May
Allah make it mubarak

276
00:34:42.391 --> 00:34:45.310
Congratulations. Nilufer Hatun.

277
00:34:45.551 --> 00:34:49.030
-Be happy. You look thoughtful.
-I'm happy.

278
00:34:49.431 --> 00:34:52.550
Not because my
husband got the title.

279
00:34:53.551 --> 00:34:58.430
But because the chair was given to someone
who can carry his dreams after Osman Bey.

280
00:34:58.751 --> 00:35:02.030
For Kayi. For all Turkmen.

281
00:35:02.271 --> 00:35:04.990
For the Islam world I'm happy.

282
00:35:08.431 --> 00:35:10.630
You should be happy too.

283
00:35:11.551 --> 00:35:15.070
If you can.

284
00:35:23.391 --> 00:35:26.710
May it be blessed. my Bey.

285
00:35:29.111 --> 00:35:32.910
O my son! Hear me.

286
00:35:33.111 --> 00:35:37.710
From now on. we may be
angry and you should fix.

287
00:35:37.951 --> 00:35:41.790
We may make mistakes
and you should correct them.

288
00:35:41.951 --> 00:35:46.030
We may break and
you should repair.

289
00:35:46.111 --> 00:35:52.110
If I break my promise. the soil
shall be watered with my blood.

290
00:35:54.631 --> 00:35:58.590
You have the sword
now. Orhan Bey

291
00:35:58.751 --> 00:36:04.990
You should decide who
will have what positions.

292
00:36:05.111 --> 00:36:09.550
My rule as well as
my beylic has fallen.

293
00:36:09.991 --> 00:36:14.990
Your rule and beylic will neither
fall nor stays on the ground...

294
00:36:15.111 --> 00:36:18.350
even If the sky
collapses; my Bey.

295
00:36:18.951 --> 00:36:20.750
You have the sanjak

296
00:36:20.991 --> 00:36:24.270
I'm just the hand holding it up.

297
00:36:25.711 --> 00:36:28.910
As to the new
positions of my Beys.

298
00:36:29.111 --> 00:36:32.870
I will consider and declare
during the sword-girding ceremony.

299
00:36:36.431 --> 00:36:38.470
Let everyone know then.

300
00:36:38.631 --> 00:36:46.030
For the beylic ceremony. all the beys
of Kayi will gather in Sogut tomorrow.

301
00:40:45.550 --> 00:40:48.109
Save the prisoners.

302
00:40:48.990 --> 00:40:52.349
Stay back. stay back.

303
00:40:53.790 --> 00:40:57.429
-Come on. come on.
-Move.

304
00:40:57.550 --> 00:40:59.989
Come on. come on.

305
00:41:00.350 --> 00:41:04.549
-May Allah be pleased with you.
-Thank you.

306
00:41:15.710 --> 00:41:18.309
You're running off. huh?

307
00:41:36.910 --> 00:41:40.789
What belongs to
Kayi will stay with Kayi.

308
00:41:44.750 --> 00:41:48.429
First. we must
tear off these rags.

309
00:41:48.590 --> 00:41:52.229
It is not enough to
just tear them off.

310
00:41:52.390 --> 00:41:55.269
We must clean this
castle from top to bottom.

311
00:41:55.790 --> 00:41:59.829
Their filthy smell has
spread everywhere.

312
00:42:00.150 --> 00:42:05.469
Come on!

313
00:42:10.390 --> 00:42:13.149
I caught these two while
they were running away.

314
00:42:17.870 --> 00:42:20.829
Just kill them.

315
00:42:21.390 --> 00:42:25.109
Wait!

316
00:42:26.910 --> 00:42:32.389
They will go and give
the news to their owner.

317
00:42:39.230 --> 00:42:43.549
You will go to Temurtas and
tell him what happened here.

318
00:42:44.070 --> 00:42:50.829
You will say that the Kayis
never forget what is done to them.

319
00:42:51.510 --> 00:42:54.789
Go now! Go!

320
00:42:54.949 --> 00:42:57.948
I will shoot arrows
behind you. It s coming'

321
00:42:58.149 --> 00:43:02.228
The arrow is going to hit you!

322
00:43:08.629 --> 00:43:13.748
Once Temurtas hears what
happened. he will lose his mind.

323
00:43:13.869 --> 00:43:16.108
Let him get mad!

324
00:43:16.589 --> 00:43:19.188
Let's celebrate our victory!

325
00:43:19.269 --> 00:43:26.468
Allah is the Greatest!
Allah is the Greatest!

326
00:43:27.949 --> 00:43:30.228
May it be mubarak. my Orhan.

327
00:43:30.429 --> 00:43:32.508
Keep praying for me. mother.

328
00:43:32.749 --> 00:43:39.428
If we received victory after victory today.
it is thanks to your brotherhood and unity.

329
00:43:39.549 --> 00:43:42.148
Let me kiss your hand mother.

330
00:43:44.269 --> 00:43:51.428
As long as this brotherhood continues. our cause
will spread to our descendants for centuries.

331
00:43:53.509 --> 00:44:00.188
To spread our thousand year
old goal. a new era will begin now.

332
00:44:00.229 --> 00:44:03.588
Fatma You go to Sogut
and start making preparations.

333
00:44:03.629 --> 00:44:06.668
In the place where we have
taken root. on the lands touched

334
00:44:06.669 --> 00:44:10.068
by the breath of Sheikh Edebali.
there will be a sword-girding ceremony.

335
00:44:10.109 --> 00:44:12.148
We will set out right
away then. brother

336
00:44:12.229 --> 00:44:15.788
We will first distribute food to the
people and give their gifts today.

337
00:44:15.789 --> 00:44:19.348
Mother... You start
gathering the tribe.

338
00:44:19.509 --> 00:44:22.708
We will migrate from here.

339
00:44:22.949 --> 00:44:24.068
Where will we go. Orhan?

340
00:44:24.149 --> 00:44:28.268
It is difficult to protect the Turkmens
who come from all sides separately.

341
00:44:29.149 --> 00:44:32.588
To stay tog ther. we will move to
the tribe on the summer pasture.

342
00:44:32.869 --> 00:44:36.428
We are going to the borders
of Bursa. It is very close to it.

343
00:44:36.589 --> 00:44:43.108
This will make it easier to keep security and also
speed up our preparations for the conquest of Bursa.

344
00:44:43.109 --> 00:44:46.588
You have thought well. my son. We
will start the preparations immediately.

345
00:44:46.629 --> 00:44:50.988
Sogut wi I be
entrusted to my Fatma.

346
00:44:58.989 --> 00:45:04.148
Long live Orhan Bey!

347
00:45:22.549 --> 00:45:28.188
Long live Orhan Bey!

348
00:45:29.189 --> 00:45:36.228
-I have good news. my Bey. Yarhisar is
Osmanogqullari's property again. -Thanks to Allah.

349
00:45:38.829 --> 00:45:41.228
Halal to those valiants.

350
00:45:41.309 --> 00:45:42.468
I have another news.

351
00:45:42.509 --> 00:45:45.828
According to the information I
received from our spies in Iznik...

352
00:45:45.869 --> 00:45:49.468
Iznik's Lord has started
making preparations for the taxes.

353
00:45:49.629 --> 00:45:52.908
He should. You also make
your preparations. Halil.

354
00:45:52.989 --> 00:45:56.948
We are now wearing
the shirt of fire.

355
00:46:17.029 --> 00:46:19.588
Hear 0. herd of infidels

356
00:46:19.629 --> 00:46:22.388
Is it easy to take
Kayis' lands?!

357
00:46:23.269 --> 00:46:26.428
Keep yelling.. Keep yelling...
You will draw the Mongols here.

358
00:46:26.469 --> 00:46:28.108
I wish I could!

359
00:46:28.109 --> 00:46:33.068
Instead of dealing with them one by one. we will
attack them all and cut them down with our swords.

360
00:46:33.149 --> 00:46:35.028
Stop talking about Mongols...

361
00:46:35.149 --> 00:46:37.388
Who has the
sanjak? Let's plant it.

362
00:46:37.389 --> 00:46:40.548
Those who did not hear
AbdurRahman's voice must all know.

363
00:46:40.709 --> 00:46:43.468
They must see that
Yarhisar belongs to Kay1!

364
00:46:43.629 --> 00:46:47.308
-I always carry it with me!
-Excellent.

365
00:47:10.669 --> 00:47:14.067
People will live in peace
under this sanjak InshaAllah.

366
00:47:14.668 --> 00:47:15.587
InshaAllah.

367
00:47:25.308 --> 00:47:31.947
Allah-u Akbar!

368
00:47:53.388 --> 00:47:57.907
Orhan... How long
have you been there?

369
00:47:58.028 --> 00:48:00.587
I can go if you want.

370
00:48:01.108 --> 00:48:03.947
Don't go...

371
00:48:29.268 --> 00:48:31.827
What happened to you?

372
00:48:38.228 --> 00:48:40.107
The Sultan of my heart...

373
00:48:40.388 --> 00:48:42.667
My pearl. my coral...

374
00:48:43.308 --> 00:48:47.707
My heart lights up in
the darkness of your hair.

375
00:48:49.348 --> 00:48:53.027
The crescent of my horizon.
your eyes are the spring of my life.

376
00:48:53.468 --> 00:48:57.147
Whenever clouds cover
them. it turns into winter.

377
00:49:03.308 --> 00:49:06.107
What happened to you? Tell me.

378
00:49:06.348 --> 00:49:08.627
I don't have any problems...

379
00:49:08.708 --> 00:49:13.547
You became the Bey... This is the happiest...
Nilufer Hatun.

380
00:49:18.508 --> 00:49:21.107
Orhan...

381
00:49:22.388 --> 00:49:27.907
It's actually not something bad.
Why aren't you telling me then?

382
00:49:29.028 --> 00:49:29.987
I...

383
00:49:34.228 --> 00:49:39.867
-I am so scared.
-What are you scared of. my beautiful wife?

384
00:49:58.708 --> 00:50:01.947
I am pregnant. Orhan.

385
00:50:07.828 --> 00:50:11.427
I am pregnant.

386
00:50:49.308 --> 00:50:52.147
Why are you telling
me this with fear?

387
00:50:52.268 --> 00:50:54.787
Ever since I heard it. I
have been really worried.

388
00:50:55.148 --> 00:50:59.387
I can't help it.. I am even
scared of being happy about it.

389
00:51:00.988 --> 00:51:05.387
After my Kasim.
we lost two children.

390
00:51:05.548 --> 00:51:08.467
-What if... -Don't be afraid.

391
00:51:08.708 --> 00:51:11.067
Nothing will happen.

392
00:51:11.668 --> 00:51:13.267
Look...

393
00:51:13.508 --> 00:51:15.707
I achieved my goal today.

394
00:51:16.148 --> 00:51:19.667
You did. I had no doubt.

395
00:51:19.988 --> 00:51:23.827
You should not have any
doubts. Don t be afraid.

396
00:51:25.068 --> 00:51:27.427
Nothing bad will happen.

397
00:51:27.588 --> 00:51:30.026
Allah saw our pain...

398
00:51:30.187 --> 00:51:32.146
and rewarded us.

399
00:51:32.347 --> 00:51:34.546
He accepted our prayers.

400
00:51:35.627 --> 00:51:42.026
You are my family that has brought
me to this position with your shadow.

401
00:51:44.387 --> 00:51:46.946
We will raise our child.

402
00:51:47.627 --> 00:51:50.426
Our wish will grow.

403
00:52:38.267 --> 00:52:41.946
Sisters!

404
00:52:51.867 --> 00:52:55.226
Fatma...

405
00:53:16.507 --> 00:53:18.826
Stop.

406
00:53:36.747 --> 00:53:39.226
You.

407
00:53:39.427 --> 00:53:42.906
Should we take him down.
Fatma Hatun®? He won't stop

408
00:53:43.747 --> 00:53:45.946
Stay out of it.

409
00:53:54.747 --> 00:53:56.906
It's destiny. Fatma Hatun.

410
00:53:57.027 --> 00:54:00.986
It's me again.

411
00:54:03.827 --> 00:54:06.986
What are you doing here.
merchant? Are you crazy?

412
00:54:07.027 --> 00:54:09.346
Do not stand in my way.
Or I will make you move.

413
00:54:09.387 --> 00:54:14.226
I should not cause
you problems...

414
00:54:28.027 --> 00:54:30.466
He is injured.

415
00:54:31.867 --> 00:54:33.546
You got injured again!

416
00:54:33.587 --> 00:54:37.306
Who did this to you?
Where were you?

417
00:54:37.827 --> 00:54:40.386
You have not forgotten it...

418
00:54:46.467 --> 00:54:49.586
It stops the bleeding.
You should learn.

419
00:54:50.507 --> 00:54:53.786
You will keep getting
injured with this impudency.

420
00:54:59.947 --> 00:55:02.826
Alps. He is badly
Injured. He passed out.

421
00:55:02.947 --> 00:55:05.826
Take him to Sogut. to
the healing tent come on!

422
00:55:21.507 --> 00:55:24.346
He should not die in our hands

423
00:55:27.587 --> 00:55:29.706
Come on!

424
00:55:30.187 --> 00:55:33.426
We wasted too much time.
Tomorrow is Kayi's biggest day.

425
00:55:33.467 --> 00:55:36.346
There will be a sword girding
ceremony for Orhan Bey.

426
00:55:36.347 --> 00:55:40.186
We have a lot to do. We will start making
preparations without missing a thing.

427
00:55:40.227 --> 00:55:43.306
Come on! Get ready!

428
00:55:47.586 --> 00:55:50.705
Come on!

429
00:56:01.906 --> 00:56:03.945
Daughter-in law!

430
00:56:04.426 --> 00:56:06.825
Come. come.

431
00:56:12.986 --> 00:56:15.505
Sit down.

432
00:56:21.506 --> 00:56:24.225
I sometimes watch
the view like this.

433
00:56:28.346 --> 00:56:32.145
Just watch. What do you see?

434
00:56:36.666 --> 00:56:40.265
My eyes see tents.

435
00:56:41.186 --> 00:56:43.905
If you ask about my heart.

436
00:56:44.506 --> 00:56:49.265
it sees the fears and
sorrow of the exhausted people.

437
00:56:55.946 --> 00:56:58.745
Yet I see one more thing.

438
00:57:03.186 --> 00:57:06.345
Unbreakable hope.

439
00:57:07.026 --> 00:57:11.905
That's it. It's exactly what
I want you to see. Nilufer.

440
00:57:12.626 --> 00:57:16.585
If you look with your
eyes. you see the crowd.

441
00:57:16.866 --> 00:57:19.585
If you look with your heart.

442
00:57:19.866 --> 00:57:22.865
you see a nation.

443
00:57:28.826 --> 00:57:32.265
Today is the beginning of
your reign. Nilufer Hatun.

444
00:57:32.706 --> 00:57:35.265
My son Orhan...

445
00:57:35.666 --> 00:57:39.065
will sit on his
father's chair.

446
00:57:40.466 --> 00:57:44.185
And you will be
the mother of Kayi.

447
00:57:45.666 --> 00:57:48.505
Now you aren t only a bride.

448
00:57:48.746 --> 00:57:50.865
but also the breath of Kayi.

449
00:57:51.146 --> 00:57:53.225
the face of the state.

450
00:57:53.586 --> 00:57:56.425
the guide of the
girls in the tribe...

451
00:57:56.586 --> 00:58:00.345
and the sharer of
your husband's burden.

452
00:58:02.466 --> 00:58:04.945
Thank you. Malhun Hatun.

453
00:58:05.666 --> 00:58:09.385
As long as I keep breathing.
I will back up Orhan.

454
00:58:09.626 --> 00:58:15.025
I know that. But I want
you to know this too.

455
00:58:16.186 --> 00:58:18.665
The beylic is such a fire...

456
00:58:18.986 --> 00:58:22.545
that there are plenty
of flames and challenges.

457
00:58:22.906 --> 00:58:26.745
You shouldn't walk in this
path only with love and heart ..

458
00:58:27.226 --> 00:58:32.065
But also with strength.
dignity and patience.

459
00:58:33.666 --> 00:58:36.065
Daughter-in-law.

460
00:58:36.226 --> 00:58:39.025
My anger wasn't
for hurting you...

461
00:58:39.266 --> 00:58:43.265
but for preparing you for
the challenge of this state.

462
00:58:52.226 --> 00:58:55.385
May Allah not let
me fail. mother.

463
00:58:58.546 --> 00:59:01.705
My girl. I'm always here.

464
00:59:01.866 --> 00:59:06.625
I will keep being your companion
and sharing your burden.

465
00:59:10.546 --> 00:59:15.025
We. mothers. exist
to make others live.

466
00:59:20.226 --> 00:59:23.985
I'm carrying a
wish inside me now.

467
00:59:24.986 --> 00:59:27.585
As I keep growing it.

468
00:59:27.786 --> 00:59:31.265
I will grow the
people you trust me for.

469
00:59:31.866 --> 00:59:36.425
May our wish be the same
with the wish of the state.

470
00:59:51.106 --> 00:59:54.985
Take this as a gift from me.

471
00:59:59.906 --> 01:00:04.305
You shall always remember
the burden you carry...

472
01:00:04.746 --> 01:00:10.104
and the trust this
state shows for you.

473
01:00:39.825 --> 01:00:44.184
-We have a busy agenda. my Bey.
-Let me take a breath first.

474
01:00:44.425 --> 01:00:46.544
I sent a message to
all the beys. my Bey.

475
01:00:46.545 --> 01:00:49.584
Everyone will attend the
sword-griding ceremony tomorrow.

476
01:00:49.585 --> 01:00:51.424
I want no mistakes

477
01:00:51.545 --> 01:00:54.584
Everyone expects us to
stumble. I want no troubles.

478
01:00:54.785 --> 01:00:58.744
With Allah's permission. you will
help this nation rise again. my Bey.

479
01:01:00.345 --> 01:01:06.024
Now. I've got informed that the gold going from
Iznik to the emperor will hit the road tomorrow.

480
01:01:06.105 --> 01:01:10.624
A second issue. Temurtas got
furious because we captured Yarhisar.

481
01:01:10.745 --> 01:01:13.664
He may attack any time.

482
01:01:15.105 --> 01:01:17.384
He must be crying
out now. right?

483
01:01:17.585 --> 01:01:20.264
And the dogs beside
him must be trembling.

484
01:01:20.545 --> 01:01:23.984
However. I haven't shown
them yet what the real fear is.

485
01:01:26.905 --> 01:01:29.624
We can't fight all those
enemies at the same time.

486
01:01:29.785 --> 01:01:32.784
Our principle is
divide and destroy.

487
01:01:33.865 --> 01:01:36.744
First. we will intimidate
Iznik helping Bursa.

488
01:01:37.025 --> 01:01:42.384
As to Temurtas. we will give him the gold we
took from Iznik and keep him away for a while.

489
01:01:42.665 --> 01:01:45.744
In the meantime. we won't
let any food enter Bursa.

490
01:01:45.945 --> 01:01:47.864
InshaAllah. my Bey.

491
01:01:48.505 --> 01:01:51.464
We need to reinforce the
alps. trade and the army.

492
01:01:51.625 --> 01:01:53.424
They are exhausted.

493
01:01:53.585 --> 01:01:56.144
We should give people hope.

494
01:01:56.945 --> 01:01:59.104
I want to consult them.

495
01:01:59.305 --> 01:02:03.464
After we repel the enemy. invite
people and the elders to my tent.

496
01:02:03.625 --> 01:02:06.224
Every change brings
another problem. my Bey.

497
01:02:06.465 --> 01:02:09.384
If we know the problem.
we can find the solution.

498
01:02:09.625 --> 01:02:13.344
We will. Halil. With
Allah's permission. we will.

499
01:02:14.065 --> 01:02:17.424
My Bey. you aren't happy
just because you got the chair.

500
01:02:17.625 --> 01:02:21.064
I know you.

501
01:02:22.585 --> 01:02:26.184
Nilufer Hatun gave
me the good news

502
01:02:27.105 --> 01:02:30.304
I will have another child.

503
01:02:34.065 --> 01:02:37.264
May your family
grow bigger. my Bey.

504
01:02:38.545 --> 01:02:41.184
May Allah give
your child a long life.

505
01:02:42.905 --> 01:02:46.864
Leave my son! Leave my son!

506
01:02:48.785 --> 01:02:51.104
Halil.

507
01:02:52.185 --> 01:02:53.984
I see and I know...

508
01:02:54.185 --> 01:02:58.184
how it hurts you whenever
someone mentions a child.

509
01:02:59.225 --> 01:03:02.504
I swear we will find your child.

510
01:03:02.785 --> 01:03:06.224
And we will destroy
who made you suffer.

511
01:03:06.425 --> 01:03:08.664
We will. my Bey

512
01:03:09.425 --> 01:03:10.504
InshaAllah.

513
01:03:23.145 --> 01:03:29.984
Turks have taken away
the breath of Bursa.

514
01:03:33.585 --> 01:03:35.904
If aid doesn't arrive.

515
01:03:36.265 --> 01:03:38.984
Bursa will be a
graveyard for all of us.

516
01:03:39.345 --> 01:03:43.584
For this reason. you
have a holy mission.

517
01:03:44.185 --> 01:03:51.664
You will send a message to Iznik.
Constantinople and even Vatican.

518
01:03:51.785 --> 01:03:54.104
Tell them to help us.

519
01:03:54.385 --> 01:04:00.264
Either they'll leave their warm
beds and we will fight together...

520
01:04:01.465 --> 01:04:04.824
or Bursa will fall.

521
01:04:05.505 --> 01:04:08.424
That won't be
good for them either.

522
01:04:08.705 --> 01:04:10.704
Will they come for
help this time. sir?

523
01:04:10.825 --> 01:04:12.904
They have to.

524
01:04:13.185 --> 01:04:20.744
Because Bursa is the castle of
Rome and Christianity in Bithynia.

525
01:04:20.825 --> 01:04:24.863
If Bursa falls.
Iznik will fall too.

526
01:04:25.264 --> 01:04:28.783
So will Constantinople.

527
01:04:30.224 --> 01:04:32.063
Make me proud.

528
01:04:32.384 --> 01:04:37.463
The future of Bursa
depends on you.

529
01:04:38.864 --> 01:04:40.903
Come on.

530
01:05:18.664 --> 01:05:20.943
I told you they would go out.

531
01:05:21.064 --> 01:05:22.343
You were right. Turahan.

532
01:05:22.544 --> 01:05:25.543
So it's my duty to beat them.

533
01:05:26.184 --> 01:05:28.783
You didn't say that. Temurboga.

534
01:05:35.584 --> 01:05:39.983
I didn't exile your father. boys.
Your father and I played a trick.

535
01:05:52.944 --> 01:05:55.343
Sit down.

536
01:05:55.584 --> 01:05:59.863
You are the head of Kayi. But
I'm still the head of the family.

537
01:06:02.744 --> 01:06:06.823
Kasim. Suleyman. come to me.

538
01:06:11.904 --> 01:06:14.903
Bismillahirrahmanirrahim.

539
01:06:23.624 --> 01:06:27.463
-Are you going somewhere. grandfather?
-No I'm here.

540
01:06:27.624 --> 01:06:29.703
Why did you leave
the tribe to my father?

541
01:06:29.904 --> 01:06:33.863
To be able to spend
more time with you.

542
01:06:34.144 --> 01:06:37.863
There is still so much to
learn from your grandfather.

543
01:06:39.664 --> 01:06:41.823
Well... I think...

544
01:06:42.064 --> 01:06:47.423
you two should be my
new Boran and Cerkutay.

545
01:06:47.704 --> 01:06:48.743
I will be Boran.

546
01:06:48.904 --> 01:06:51.143
-No. I will be Boran.
-No. I will be Boran.

547
01:06:51.264 --> 01:06:52.743
I will be Boran!

548
01:06:53.224 --> 01:06:56.743
My Allah! Why don't you
want to be Cerkutay. boys?

549
01:06:56.904 --> 01:07:00.783
He shouldn t know about
this. He would be jealous!

550
01:07:03.224 --> 01:07:08.343
As long as we stand united
like this. no troubles can harm us.

551
01:07:13.344 --> 01:07:17.943
We want to give some more good news
to bring joy and fertility in this table.

552
01:07:20.744 --> 01:07:24.663
Nilufer and I will
have another child.

553
01:07:25.544 --> 01:07:28.263
Allah! I'm becoming an
elder brother second time!

554
01:07:28.344 --> 01:07:30.463
You're being an elder
brother too. Kasim.

555
01:07:30.504 --> 01:07:32.663
Good. We will
be a bigger family.

556
01:07:32.824 --> 01:07:35.783
So we can share the
duties. right. brother?

557
01:07:41.544 --> 01:07:46.503
Thanks to Allah. Another
child means another family.

558
01:07:46.744 --> 01:07:51.703
May it bring happiness to our
tribe and bless to our house. son.

559
01:07:52.184 --> 01:07:53.583
-Aameen.
-Aameen.

560
01:07:53.824 --> 01:07:55.263
-Aameen.
-Aameen.

561
01:07:55.464 --> 01:07:57.783
May Allah give it
a long life. dear.

562
01:07:58.024 --> 01:08:01.543
-Aameen. mother.
-May it be blessed. brother.

563
01:08:01.944 --> 01:08:06.263
-Thanks. brother.
-May Allah give you healthy baby. Nilufer.

564
01:08:06.544 --> 01:08:08.743
Thanks. Gonca. InshaAllah.

565
01:08:09.224 --> 01:08:11.303
Uncle Alaeddin
Yes??

566
01:08:11.544 --> 01:08:14.663
When will you have a baby?

567
01:08:20.424 --> 01:08:25.303
When you have a baby. we
can't fit in this table. grandfather.

568
01:08:28.704 --> 01:08:32.143
There is a time
for each child. dear.

569
01:08:32.464 --> 01:08:35.463
That time will arrive
too. InshaAllah.

570
01:08:36.584 --> 01:08:38.983
-InshaAllah.
-InshaAllah.

571
01:08:42.103 --> 01:08:44.022
Here we go.

572
01:08:44.463 --> 01:08:47.022
Enjoy your meal.

573
01:09:00.983 --> 01:09:03.782
Attack!

574
01:09:22.303 --> 01:09:25.262
You're rusted. brother.
You say so. brother?

575
01:09:26.023 --> 01:09:28.382
Catch up with me.

576
01:09:45.503 --> 01:09:50.062
Orhan Bey's order is certain. The
only way to leave Bursa is to surrender.

577
01:09:50.263 --> 01:09:52.822
We will even shoot
the flying birds.

578
01:10:00.343 --> 01:10:03.222
Saroz!

579
01:10:07.903 --> 01:10:11.862
You will either
surrender or die!

580
01:10:12.743 --> 01:10:15.102
No!

581
01:10:16.063 --> 01:10:19.262
No!

582
01:10:19.263 --> 01:10:25.582
Orhan! Orhan!

583
01:10:35.943 --> 01:10:43.742
I swear on the tent on the
ground and the throne in the sky.

584
01:10:44.023 --> 01:10:46.182
I am Sahinshah.

585
01:10:46.423 --> 01:10:48.982
Kinik's honorable Bey.

586
01:10:49.023 --> 01:10:56.782
To protect the future on these lands. the
honor and dignity I inherited from my father...

587
01:10:57.623 --> 01:11:01.342
and to take what
belongs to me...

588
01:11:01.423 --> 01:11:05.782
I will fight until my
last breath if necessary...

589
01:11:06.103 --> 01:11:09.902
and I will
sacrifice my last Alp.

590
01:11:21.943 --> 01:11:29.022
If I turn from my path. may the
dagger I cut my hair with stab my heart.

591
01:12:02.383 --> 01:12:05.862
They act like you are not here.

592
01:12:06.663 --> 01:12:09.342
They act as if
you never existed.

593
01:12:09.743 --> 01:12:12.822
Nothing really hurts...

594
01:12:13.623 --> 01:12:16.982
but my Yigit
uniting with them...

595
01:12:17.863 --> 01:12:19.542
He is an Alp.

596
01:12:20.543 --> 01:12:25.382
He must stand by his
Bey's. his Commander's side.

597
01:12:26.023 --> 01:12:28.382
My heart is burning in flames...

598
01:12:28.583 --> 01:12:31.022
but I am not saying a thing.

599
01:12:31.463 --> 01:12:36.622
What makes me suffer is that...

600
01:12:36.863 --> 01:12:41.102
Osman Bey does not say a
single thing when all this is happening.

601
01:12:42.903 --> 01:12:46.662
Ah my Sahinshah..

602
01:12:47.463 --> 01:12:54.782
You. the greatest heir of the
Seljuks. the mighty Bey of the Kinik.

603
01:12:56.143 --> 01:13:00.701
The leader of the rebellion
against the Ilkhanids...

604
01:13:04.262 --> 01:13:11.301
My wounded lion who
gave up himself for Kay..

605
01:13:18.062 --> 01:13:24.141
Osman i1s taking your son from you when he can
even give the Beylic to you since you deserve it.

606
01:13:27.142 --> 01:13:30.661
Is this what you deserve?

607
01:13:31.502 --> 01:13:34.541
It's not Didar Hatun.

608
01:13:34.702 --> 01:13:36.981
It's not.

609
01:13:37.542 --> 01:13:46.741
Will you accept being sacrificed for his sons
by Osman Bey for whom you gave up everything?

610
01:13:50.022 --> 01:13:54.461
I will accept it. but
they will understand.

611
01:13:55.742 --> 01:13:59.501
And that day is not far.

612
01:14:35.582 --> 01:14:38.781
How is the merchant?

613
01:14:38.982 --> 01:14:41.661
He is still asleep.

614
01:14:53.982 --> 01:14:57.861
Those who look at him
might think he is strong.

615
01:14:59.302 --> 01:15:04.461
He passed out with
a dagger wound.

616
01:15:07.062 --> 01:15:09.181
It looks like he
is not breathing.

617
01:15:09.222 --> 01:15:11.941
-Call the doctor here!
-As you order. Fatma Hatun.

618
01:15:43.542 --> 01:15:46.021
I am not dead. Don't be scared

619
01:15:47.582 --> 01:15:49.861
Why would I be scared?

620
01:15:49.942 --> 01:15:51.901
I don't care.

621
01:15:52.782 --> 01:15:54.581
You were scared.

622
01:15:54.782 --> 01:15:58.901
I heard everything
you said there.

623
01:15:59.942 --> 01:16:03.661
-Look at me. you impudent man...
-Sure I'll look...

624
01:16:05.822 --> 01:16:08.901
I'll look at you. but...

625
01:16:08.982 --> 01:16:12.981
what I am seeing is
surprising. Fatma Hatun.

626
01:16:14.182 --> 01:16:20.181
I didn't know you were cruel enough to point
your dagger at someone who is already wounded.

627
01:16:25.262 --> 01:16:31.301
This is nothing. If you keep going
that far. you will then see my cruelty.

628
01:16:31.462 --> 01:16:33.301
Speak now.

629
01:16:33.982 --> 01:16:36.181
Who did this to you?

630
01:16:36.702 --> 01:16:39.741
Their faces were covered.
I guess they were thieves.

631
01:16:40.062 --> 01:16:42.941
But you should've
seen what I did to them.

632
01:16:43.222 --> 01:16:44.981
I took a few of them down...

633
01:16:46.022 --> 01:16:48.181
But there were many of them.

634
01:16:51.422 --> 01:16:55.181
How did they leave you
with only one wound?

635
01:16:55.862 --> 01:16:59.261
I left my goods behind and ran away
with my horse... You know the rest.

636
01:17:00.742 --> 01:17:03.181
I am Allah's loved servant...

637
01:17:03.342 --> 01:17:06.141
Since He let you find me.

638
01:17:10.062 --> 01:17:12.821
I owe you my life Fatma Hatun.

639
01:17:15.301 --> 01:17:17.780
Good.

640
01:17:17.901 --> 01:17:20.620
We will get even in due time.

641
01:17:21.421 --> 01:17:23.420
We will.

642
01:17:24.541 --> 01:17:27.260
Sister!

643
01:17:27.301 --> 01:17:29.940
Sister...

644
01:17:36.181 --> 01:17:38.140
The doctor is coming.

645
01:17:38.421 --> 01:17:40.980
You can shout if
you need something.

646
01:17:41.341 --> 01:17:44.060
Thank you.

647
01:17:55.341 --> 01:17:57.620
Come on!

648
01:18:05.381 --> 01:18:09.020
Write it down. AbdurRahman'
It is four against four now'

649
01:18:10.821 --> 01:18:13.780
Come on now!

650
01:18:18.221 --> 01:18:20.500
Come on!

651
01:18:20.581 --> 01:18:22.660
Come on! Stop waiting!

652
01:18:28.901 --> 01:18:32.260
Write it down!
Half for Kanturali!

653
01:18:32.541 --> 01:18:35.660
He poured half of it!

654
01:18:35.981 --> 01:18:38.660
Drink water.
brother! Drink water!

655
01:18:39.901 --> 01:18:42.420
Drink some water! Come on!

656
01:18:45.741 --> 01:18:48.900
My valiant.. Brother...

657
01:18:48.981 --> 01:18:52.020
We ran out of molasses but
they are still strong Cerkutay..

658
01:18:52.101 --> 01:18:54.820
I will not give up!
MashaAllah to my valiant

659
01:18:54.861 --> 01:18:57.180
Fill the cup! Fill it!

660
01:19:16.101 --> 01:19:17.780
Cerkutay. look at him..

661
01:19:18.101 --> 01:19:21.460
What is our brother looking at?
He might have seen the Azrael.

662
01:19:21.461 --> 01:19:24.340
He is about to give the
trust back to its Owner soon.

663
01:19:24.581 --> 01:19:26.140
Look at his eyes...

664
01:19:27.261 --> 01:19:30.940
This molasses is really sweet...

665
01:19:37.101 --> 01:19:39.780
MashaAllah to you!

666
01:19:40.221 --> 01:19:43.660
You are the best among the
warriors. AbdurRahman brother.

667
01:19:44.021 --> 01:19:46.020
This is not even my best!

668
01:19:46.101 --> 01:19:49.380
I can even drink ten more cups!

669
01:19:49.541 --> 01:19:52.460
AbdurRahman don't brother...

670
01:19:52.541 --> 01:19:54.660
I can drink ten more...
Brother don't..

671
01:19:55.021 --> 01:19:57.340
I finally found myself a rival.

672
01:19:57.821 --> 01:20:00.260
You should compete
with me. brother.

673
01:20:00.741 --> 01:20:03.060
Brother...

674
01:20:09.661 --> 01:20:14.740
-We should attack the infidel with molasses...
-We should brother...

675
01:20:15.061 --> 01:20:19.020
Kanturali. what are you
doing on the ground?

676
01:20:22.461 --> 01:20:25.860
I am watching the
stars. Kara Hallil.

677
01:20:27.661 --> 01:20:30.660
-Lift him up. -Come on brother.

678
01:20:31.861 --> 01:20:34.340
Welcome. my Kara Halil.

679
01:20:35.701 --> 01:20:38.100
Kara Halil. Where
is my Orhan Bey?

680
01:20:38.181 --> 01:20:39.580
Why didn't he come?

681
01:20:39.661 --> 01:20:43.660
Orhan Bey received two
good news In one day.

682
01:20:45.941 --> 01:20:48.740
Therefore. he'll
stay with his family.

683
01:20:49.421 --> 01:20:50.900
We know one of them.

684
01:20:51.301 --> 01:20:53.340
But we don t
know the other one.

685
01:20:53.741 --> 01:20:57.380
I cannot think properly..
Just tell us already!

686
01:20:57.781 --> 01:20:59.340
Allah accepted prayers...

687
01:20:59.661 --> 01:21:01.620
and my Bey will
have another child.

688
01:21:03.701 --> 01:21:07.540
-MashaAllah!
-Hay MashaAllah!

689
01:21:07.621 --> 01:21:09.700
This is really good news!

690
01:21:09.941 --> 01:21:13.620
So another valiant will
join the other two. huh?

691
01:21:13.821 --> 01:21:16.460
I feel sorry for
the infidels now...

692
01:21:17.461 --> 01:21:19.780
Orhan Bey has
assigned duties for you.

693
01:21:20.221 --> 01:21:22.180
I should tell you that first.

694
01:21:22.941 --> 01:21:24.180
My Cerkutay Bey.

695
01:21:24.621 --> 01:21:26.180
It is my Orhan Bey's order.

696
01:21:26.421 --> 01:21:28.820
Tomorrow. you will
go to Iznik as an envoy.

697
01:21:29.301 --> 01:21:32.659
You will tell the Lord of
Iznik that my Bey will go there.

698
01:21:33.020 --> 01:21:35.899
I ll do as Orhan Bey says.

699
01:21:36.100 --> 01:21:37.699
AbdurRahman. Kanturali...

700
01:21:37.900 --> 01:21:41.179
Taxes will go to the
Emperor from Iznik tomorrow.

701
01:21:41.340 --> 01:21:47.339
While my Bey draws all the attention when speaking with
the Lord. you will raid the caravan and take the gold.

702
01:21:48.020 --> 01:21:49.539
Thanks to Allah.

703
01:21:49.620 --> 01:21:54.299
Instead of seeing the ugly face of
that Lord. we will beat his soldiers!

704
01:21:54.620 --> 01:21:56.059
Kara Halil.

705
01:21:56.260 --> 01:21:58.379
Tell my Bey...

706
01:21:58.460 --> 01:22:01.579
A suitable Hatun for our
AbdurRahman must be found. huh?

707
01:22:01.740 --> 01:22:05.299
Watch your words. Kantural!

708
01:22:06.700 --> 01:22:08.219
Watch your words...

709
01:22:09.140 --> 01:22:11.259
Watch your words...

710
01:22:11.420 --> 01:22:13.579
It's because of the molasses...

711
01:22:19.820 --> 01:22:23.619
Balaban. Dumrul. Come on.

712
01:22:36.860 --> 01:22:39.179
There is no need for a cup!

713
01:22:41.860 --> 01:22:45.619
What is he doing?

714
01:22:56.980 --> 01:22:59.699
Didn't you have
something to do in the tribe?

715
01:22:59.820 --> 01:23:01.419
Why did you come after me?

716
01:23:01.460 --> 01:23:03.699
I did not want to
leave my sister alone.

717
01:23:03.700 --> 01:23:05.179
Did I do wrong?

718
01:23:05.500 --> 01:23:07.299
You did well.

719
01:23:07.420 --> 01:23:10.379
-My mother knows. right?
-She does.

720
01:23:11.300 --> 01:23:15.019
So... I heard you've
been saving lives.

721
01:23:16.220 --> 01:23:19.379
First. Yigit Bey.. And
now that merchant...

722
01:23:19.700 --> 01:23:23.139
I've been thinking about it
since that day in the river. sister.

723
01:23:23.220 --> 01:23:25.099
You are trying to hide it but..

724
01:23:25.300 --> 01:23:28.179
Who is that merchant? Tell me;.

725
01:23:29.700 --> 01:23:30.739
Halime...

726
01:23:31.420 --> 01:23:34.259
I don't know.. He was just
an injured merchant. Halime.

727
01:23:34.380 --> 01:23:36.419
How would I know? I
don't know who he is.

728
01:23:36.460 --> 01:23:39.779
Why are you asking
me these questions?

729
01:23:39.820 --> 01:23:41.739
Kayi's girls admire Yigit Bey...

730
01:23:42.540 --> 01:23:45.099
But Yigit Bey admires you.

731
01:23:45.260 --> 01:23:47.899
The merchant also
admires you sister.

732
01:23:48.420 --> 01:23:51.499
Everyone admires someone..

733
01:23:51.620 --> 01:23:54.459
But I wonder who you admire.

734
01:23:55.060 --> 01:23:57.419
You are too bad...

735
01:23:57.500 --> 01:24:01.099
Once you notice
something. you keep insisting!

736
01:24:03.380 --> 01:24:07.339
I never admired
someone and I won't!

737
01:24:10.060 --> 01:24:14.859
But your face is telling me a different
story. sister. You are blushing already.

738
01:24:17.820 --> 01:24:19.339
Enough!

739
01:24:19.460 --> 01:24:23.379
I'll go to sleep. And you will go to
the tribe early in the morning. Come on!

740
01:24:23.780 --> 01:24:26.979
Good night.

741
01:24:31.780 --> 01:24:33.859
Sister...

742
01:24:34.340 --> 01:24:38.699
My mother is still looking for
grooms. you know that right?

743
01:24:41.820 --> 01:24:45.259
If you love someone...

744
01:25:02.580 --> 01:25:06.059
Have a good night sister.

745
01:25:20.580 --> 01:25:22.939
I tried everything.

746
01:25:23.900 --> 01:25:26.179
Everything.

747
01:25:29.580 --> 01:25:31.059
Gonca.

748
01:25:34.860 --> 01:25:37.099
My Gonca.

749
01:25:41.340 --> 01:25:44.139
What are you doing. my dear?

750
01:25:49.260 --> 01:25:52.538
For years.

751
01:25:54.699 --> 01:26:03.378
I've placed my
hope on these herbs.

752
01:26:04.659 --> 01:26:06.578
It's over.

753
01:26:07.019 --> 01:26:11.058
See? I burned them all.

754
01:26:11.859 --> 01:26:15.658
I've left no maybes
for me. Alaeddin.

755
01:26:15.899 --> 01:26:18.778
My gazelle eyed wife.

756
01:26:19.059 --> 01:26:21.018
Pretty-faced wife.

757
01:26:21.379 --> 01:26:23.618
My life.

758
01:26:23.979 --> 01:26:28.538
A child is a gift
from Allah. hatun.

759
01:26:29.299 --> 01:26:34.058
We accept whatever
our fate is. huh?

760
01:26:41.619 --> 01:26:45.018
Not you. I will.

761
01:26:46.979 --> 01:26:49.418
I will accept.

762
01:26:50.219 --> 01:26:52.658
You are Osman Bey's son.

763
01:26:52.899 --> 01:26:58.098
It's your duty to continue
your blood. Alaeddin.

764
01:27:03.619 --> 01:27:05.658
What do you mean?

765
01:27:06.419 --> 01:27:09.538
There is no you and me.
hatun. There is only us.

766
01:27:09.659 --> 01:27:11.538
Nothing else just us.

767
01:27:11.699 --> 01:27:14.058
Nothing else.

768
01:27:15.979 --> 01:27:18.018
Nothing else.

769
01:27:18.699 --> 01:27:21.098
Don't upset yourself anymore.

770
01:27:21.579 --> 01:27:24.618
Stop upsetting yourself. Gonca.

771
01:27:25.459 --> 01:27:30.378
Alaeddin. I thought too much...

772
01:27:32.299 --> 01:27:36.538
I resisted. Alaeddin.
I always resisted.

773
01:27:37.259 --> 01:27:41.058
Well... I always hoped.

774
01:27:41.579 --> 01:27:43.538
But no.

775
01:27:44.179 --> 01:27:47.458
There are no other options.

776
01:27:47.899 --> 01:27:50.738
What do you mean”?

777
01:27:52.699 --> 01:27:58.618
Malhun Hatun told Didar Hatun...

778
01:27:59.299 --> 01:28:03.178
to find someone who
can give baby to you.

779
01:28:06.819 --> 01:28:08.618
What?

780
01:28:08.939 --> 01:28:10.538
How so?

781
01:28:10.779 --> 01:28:12.618
How could my mother do this?

782
01:28:12.859 --> 01:28:16.538
-Oh mother! Oh mother
-I accept this.

783
01:28:18.339 --> 01:28:21.058
I accept this.

784
01:28:21.739 --> 01:28:25.178
What are you
talking about. Gonca?

785
01:28:25.979 --> 01:28:28.258
-Avci Bey's daughter.
-And?

786
01:28:28.459 --> 01:28:31.458
Colpan. She is suitable for you.

787
01:28:31.659 --> 01:28:33.858
Enough

788
01:28:35.179 --> 01:28:38.058
Look at me. Look!

789
01:28:39.179 --> 01:28:41.938
Did we swear for
love In vain. hatun?

790
01:28:42.099 --> 01:28:45.538
Alaeddin. don't do this
Have we fought so far in vain?

791
01:28:45.699 --> 01:28:49.618
Don't. Don t.
Gonca. my dear. No.

792
01:28:50.659 --> 01:28:53.898
I don't want to hear such
things from you again.

793
01:28:54.339 --> 01:28:56.858
-Never.
-Alaeddin.

794
01:28:57.179 --> 01:28:59.858
What would change
if I said alright?

795
01:29:00.219 --> 01:29:02.778
What would change. Alaeddin?

796
01:29:03.019 --> 01:29:04.218
Tell me.

797
01:29:04.339 --> 01:29:07.658
Would my fate
change then? Tell me.

798
01:29:11.019 --> 01:29:16.698
You have the right to have a baby. Alaeddin.
What would change if I said alright?

799
01:29:19.579 --> 01:29:23.058
Enough Gonca.
Stop crying. Please.

800
01:29:23.299 --> 01:29:27.258
-Don't do this.
-Please.

801
01:29:34.499 --> 01:29:37.178
I don't want to hear
that again hatun

802
01:29:37.499 --> 01:29:40.578
I don't want to hear that again.

803
01:29:56.019 --> 01:29:58.738
Forgive us. Temurtas.
We made a mistake.

804
01:29:58.859 --> 01:30:02.858
Spare our lives. Mighty Temurtas.
Please forgive us.

805
01:30:19.418 --> 01:30:24.217
Thos who surrendered
Yarhisar to Orhan's alps...

806
01:30:24.418 --> 01:30:27.737
have no place beside me!

807
01:30:40.338 --> 01:30:43.897
Pigeon has brought a
message. Governor Temurtas.

808
01:30:54.858 --> 01:30:58.097
Orhan offers a deal.

809
01:31:00.178 --> 01:31:04.937
He attacked Yarhisar
and killed my nokers.

810
01:31:05.218 --> 01:31:09.057
How could he offer a
deal with no shame?

811
01:31:12.658 --> 01:31:15.937
Send your messengers. Orhan.

812
01:31:16.898 --> 01:31:20.577
I will have a nice
deal with them.

813
01:31:27.978 --> 01:31:31.377
I will change the fate you
determined for my people.

814
01:31:32.338 --> 01:31:35.057
Are you available. Akcora?

815
01:31:38.978 --> 01:31:42.017
I will kill my biggest enemy
thanks to you. Fatma.

816
01:31:42.298 --> 01:31:43.937
Akcora?

817
01:31:44.218 --> 01:31:46.577
Come in.

818
01:31:56.938 --> 01:31:58.857
What is it?

819
01:31:59.098 --> 01:32:01.657
What are you grinning for?

820
01:32:02.258 --> 01:32:04.417
I see the angel
who saved my life.

821
01:32:04.538 --> 01:32:06.777
How can I not smile?

822
01:32:07.458 --> 01:32:08.937
You're exaggerating.

823
01:32:09.098 --> 01:32:11.057
Your wound wasn't so serious.

824
01:32:11.258 --> 01:32:13.057
I'm just a tradesman.

825
01:32:13.258 --> 01:32:16.697
That wound was too much for me.

826
01:32:17.338 --> 01:32:18.857
You are so fragile.

827
01:32:19.058 --> 01:32:22.377
You aren't ke any other
women I have ever seen.

828
01:32:22.658 --> 01:32:26.337
Women are fragile
and weak. but you...

829
01:32:26.938 --> 01:32:29.057
You are strong.

830
01:32:29.538 --> 01:32:32.377
You say you met many women?

831
01:32:33.098 --> 01:32:35.057
I sell fabrics. you know.

832
01:32:35.498 --> 01:32:38.057
That's why. There
were no other reasons.

833
01:32:38.258 --> 01:32:42.617
I don't have a fiancee or
anyone else waiting for me.

834
01:32:50.018 --> 01:32:53.177
I didn't ask you.

835
01:32:55.338 --> 01:33:00.977
I didn't come to ask about people waiting
for you but people who attacked you.

836
01:33:06.058 --> 01:33:10.497
Fatma Hatun. Orhan Bey
and Osman Bey are here.

837
01:33:34.218 --> 01:33:36.097
What's happening in Bursa?

838
01:33:36.178 --> 01:33:38.337
Orhan found and
destroyed the tunnels.

839
01:33:38.378 --> 01:33:40.577
Nobody can enter or
leave Bursa anymore.

840
01:33:40.578 --> 01:33:42.737
People are starving to death.

841
01:33:42.938 --> 01:33:44.657
What do you say?

842
01:33:44.778 --> 01:33:49.137
Should we recruit an
army and attack Orhan?

843
01:33:49.338 --> 01:33:51.097
We have to. Lord Leon.

844
01:33:51.298 --> 01:33:53.577
If Bursa falls. Iznik will fall.

845
01:33:53.698 --> 01:33:56.297
Iznik is the gate opening
to Constantinople.

846
01:33:56.538 --> 01:33:58.377
Who could stop Turks then?

847
01:33:58.538 --> 01:34:01.177
We need to help Bursa.

848
01:34:07.098 --> 01:34:11.457
My Lord. Orhan Bey's
messenger wants to see you.

849
01:34:18.738 --> 01:34:23.177
Wow. wow. wow.

850
01:34:29.377 --> 01:34:32.816
Have a good day. Lord Leon.

851
01:34:32.977 --> 01:34:40.216
I've brought the regards and greetings
for Orhan Bey. the courageous Bey of Kay|.

852
01:34:40.737 --> 01:34:44.216
Let's get to know each
other. Who are you?

853
01:34:45.217 --> 01:34:47.496
I'm just Cerkutay.

854
01:34:47.617 --> 01:34:51.576
who became a Turk
while a Mongolian.

855
01:34:51.777 --> 01:34:56.856
who found peace in Islam and
who is Orhan Bey's messenger now.

856
01:34:57.537 --> 01:34:59.336
Nice to meet you

857
01:34:59.497 --> 01:35:01.176
I'm all ears.

858
01:35:01.417 --> 01:35:03.416
Orhan Bey is going to come here.

859
01:35:03.657 --> 01:35:05.296
Why?

860
01:35:05.737 --> 01:35:09.536
He will check your eyebrows
eyes and your unlovely...

861
01:35:09.537 --> 01:35:15.336
I mean your pretty face spreading
love around and your pulse...

862
01:35:22.137 --> 01:35:23.976
and make a decision.

863
01:35:24.257 --> 01:35:25.656
What decision?

864
01:35:25.777 --> 01:35:27.736
I don't know. My Bey knows.

865
01:35:28.057 --> 01:35:31.136
But I know this.

866
01:35:31.537 --> 01:35:36.736
Orhan Bey must be
treated well and nicely.

867
01:35:37.057 --> 01:35:40.136
If he doesn't get pleased.

868
01:35:41.017 --> 01:35:44.376
it won't be
good for you at all.

869
01:35:45.537 --> 01:35:48.056
I should go now.

870
01:35:50.977 --> 01:35:55.696
Also. Orhan Bey wants to see...

871
01:35:55.897 --> 01:35:59.856
the prominent
noble men of Iznik.

872
01:36:00.217 --> 01:36:03.536
-What for?
-For.

873
01:36:04.777 --> 01:36:08.096
You can ask Orhan Bey.

874
01:37:04.817 --> 01:37:08.696
I will miss this.
This excitement.

875
01:37:08.897 --> 01:37:13.576
-My children beside me..
-Not so fast. We have yet to enter Bursa together.

876
01:37:16.777 --> 01:37:19.656
Here we go.

877
01:37:26.817 --> 01:37:30.176
-Welcome to our capital city. my Bey.
-Thanks. girl.

878
01:37:30.337 --> 01:37:32.816
Brother Orhan. Brother Alaeddin.

879
01:37:32.937 --> 01:37:35.656
Our capital city for now.

880
01:37:36.297 --> 01:37:39.696
You came a long way. Get some
rest. We prepared a table for Beys.

881
01:37:39.857 --> 01:37:41.576
Well done. girl.

882
01:37:41.737 --> 01:37:44.376
What's the situation?
Is everything alright?

883
01:37:44.457 --> 01:37:45.896
No problem. brother

884
01:37:46.017 --> 01:37:49.216
A bandit attacked a
tradesman and wounded him.

885
01:37:49.217 --> 01:37:51.176
Is he alright? We
can check his wound.

886
01:37:51.177 --> 01:37:52.656
Doctors took care of him.

887
01:37:52.697 --> 01:37:55.616
I as-signed some
alps to find the bandit.

888
01:37:55.977 --> 01:37:58.816
Well done. Let's
go to the council.

889
01:37:58.977 --> 01:38:01.096
Well... You go.

890
01:38:01.337 --> 01:38:02.696
Father.

891
01:38:03.017 --> 01:38:04.496
Are you not coming?

892
01:38:04.657 --> 01:38:08.856
Now you are to rule the
councils and give orders. son.

893
01:38:09.217 --> 01:38:11.536
I will do my part.

894
01:38:11.777 --> 01:38:14.776
Chat with people.

895
01:38:14.937 --> 01:38:15.896
As you order.

896
01:38:15.897 --> 01:38:20.296
-Long live Osman Bey.
-Thanks. thanks. How are you doing?

897
01:38:20.617 --> 01:38:22.976
-Welcome. my Bey.
-Thanks. How are you doing?

898
01:38:23.097 --> 01:38:25.296
-Thanks.
-Osman Bey. welcome.

899
01:38:25.457 --> 01:38:28.776
-Long live Osman Bey!
-Are you fine?

900
01:38:57.976 --> 01:39:02.375
Why did you cut the hair you've been
growing for ten years. Sahinshah Bey?

901
01:39:02.656 --> 01:39:06.735
Wasn't it the mark
of your victories”

902
01:39:08.496 --> 01:39:11.535
You are right. my
Bey. You are right.

903
01:39:11.896 --> 01:39:18.895
When I first found Osman Bey. it had been burned
In the last battle we fought against the Ilkhanids.

904
01:39:19.776 --> 01:39:24.255
Now I will start again with you.

905
01:39:24.616 --> 01:39:29.855
May Allah grant us another ten years of
fighting side by side and growing it again.

906
01:39:30.816 --> 01:39:34.575
-Aameen.
-Aameen

907
01:39:37.096 --> 01:39:40.255
My Beys. Let s talk
about your duties.

908
01:39:41.136 --> 01:39:46.695
I have put my brother Alaeddin in charge of
making all the state institutions work properly.

909
01:39:47.936 --> 01:39:53.815
But in the lands where we live together with the
Oghuz tribes. we will first build our unity with you.

910
01:39:54.016 --> 01:39:55.935
Sahinshah Bey.

911
01:39:56.056 --> 01:39:59.775
You are responsible for checking
and strengthening the fortresses.

912
01:40:01.376 --> 01:40:06.375
Avci Bey. You are responsible for the order
of the summer and winter fields of the tribes.

913
01:40:07.256 --> 01:40:11.375
Wherever you believe we can be
useful. that is where we will be. my Bey.

914
01:40:11.536 --> 01:40:14.815
Just order us. my Bey.

915
01:40:20.456 --> 01:40:26.255
My first command is for my
brother Alaeddin and Sahinshah Bey.

916
01:40:26.736 --> 01:40:33.015
Your duty will be to make peace with the dog
called Temurtas until the right time comes.

917
01:40:37.616 --> 01:40:45.535
My Bey... Temurtas is very angry
after what you did in Yarhisar.

918
01:40:45.736 --> 01:40:49.255
Alaeddin and Sahinshah
Bey will handle it. Avci Bey.

919
01:40:49.376 --> 01:40:52.895
You will support
them with your Alps.

920
01:40:56.616 --> 01:41:00.815
They will make him an
offer he cannot refuse.

921
01:41:01.856 --> 01:41:05.655
As for the other Beys...

922
01:41:32.416 --> 01:41:36.415
Orhan became the Bey of Kay|.

923
01:41:36.936 --> 01:41:40.855
There will be a ceremony In
Sogut. What are we going to do. sir?

924
01:41:42.256 --> 01:41:44.095
Osman will die tonight.

925
01:41:44.216 --> 01:41:47.655
With my poisonous arrow.
As he killed my father ..

926
01:41:47.816 --> 01:41:49.575
I will kill him.

927
01:41:49.736 --> 01:41:52.375
Blood for blood.

928
01:41:52.536 --> 01:41:54.375
Therefore. Bursa will be saved.

929
01:41:54.456 --> 01:41:56.495
Sir. we don't have
enough men with us.

930
01:41:56.696 --> 01:41:58.455
What if you get caught?

931
01:41:58.536 --> 01:42:01.495
Then I'll go to heaven

932
01:42:01.536 --> 01:42:06.135
But death will find
Kayis today. not me

933
01:42:07.216 --> 01:42:09.175
If I cannot complete
what I start...

934
01:42:09.536 --> 01:42:12.655
you will finish it for me.

935
01:42:13.816 --> 01:42:18.855
You are the last
warriors of Bursa.

936
01:42:47.976 --> 01:42:50.975
Welcome..

937
01:42:51.096 --> 01:42:55.455
Thank you. Thank you.

938
01:43:08.895 --> 01:43:11.854
Thank you.

939
01:43:16.535 --> 01:43:18.414
My Bey welcome.

940
01:43:18.735 --> 01:43:21.294
Ghazi Ahmed. How are you?

941
01:43:21.455 --> 01:43:24.654
Thank you. I am
praying for your health.

942
01:43:25.735 --> 01:43:32.694
I heard that you want the veteran
relief to be taken away from you.

943
01:43:32.815 --> 01:43:36.014
I just have my life. my Bey.
And it will be full with one bite.

944
01:43:36.215 --> 01:43:38.614
Send that aid to Bursa...

945
01:43:39.015 --> 01:43:41.134
to those at the front.

946
01:43:41.255 --> 01:43:46.414
No... You deserve that.

947
01:43:46.735 --> 01:43:49.774
Just pray...

948
01:43:49.895 --> 01:43:52.334
For the existence of our
nation and our dreams...

949
01:43:52.535 --> 01:43:55.534
keep praying.
I am always praying.

950
01:43:56.015 --> 01:44:01.174
I am praying for you. and your son Orhan
who is now sitting on the chair of Beylic.

951
01:44:01.295 --> 01:44:05.614
Your son Orhan has
the foresight of Sultans

952
01:44:06.015 --> 01:44:09.654
InshaAllah he will be the hope of
poor Turkmens who do not have a state.

953
01:44:11.095 --> 01:44:15.574
Thank you Ghazi. Thank you.

954
01:44:21.135 --> 01:44:23.894
Slow down!
I didn't see you. my Hanim.

955
01:44:24.015 --> 01:44:25.534
Forgive me.

956
01:44:25.815 --> 01:44:28.574
Go and do your job. Go.

957
01:44:28.775 --> 01:44:31.414
Father!

958
01:44:36.095 --> 01:44:39.094
Father... The
ceremony will begin now.

959
01:44:39.215 --> 01:44:41.094
Come on then.

960
01:44:41.895 --> 01:44:45.614
-Safely. Ghazi. -Thank you.

961
01:45:35.975 --> 01:45:40.334
Attention! Osman Bey!

962
01:45:44.335 --> 01:45:48.574
Long hive Osman Bey!

963
01:45:48.895 --> 01:45:52.574
Thank you. Long live Osman Bey!

964
01:46:01.015 --> 01:46:04.654
Long live Osman Bey!

965
01:46:05.535 --> 01:46:10.174
Long live Osman Bey!

966
01:46:10.575 --> 01:46:16.054
Long live my Bey!

967
01:46:22.895 --> 01:46:26.614
-Long live my Bey!
-Thank you. Thank you.

968
01:47:06.695 --> 01:47:13.014
In the past. my father Ertugrul
Ghazi received the symbols of Beylic...

969
01:47:13.095 --> 01:47:18.133
for his Beylic from
the Sultan of Konya.

970
01:47:18.254 --> 01:47:23.693
Now those symbols will
be given to Orhan Bey.

971
01:47:25.054 --> 01:47:28.613
Bring the tails of the Beylic!

972
01:47:34.854 --> 01:47:40.093
May you always keep
this tail raised. my son.

973
01:47:40.254 --> 01:47:44.093
Come on. give the sanjak to him.

974
01:48:06.734 --> 01:48:12.693
The sanjak represents
the honour of a state.

975
01:48:12.774 --> 01:48:16.653
Fly it with honour. -Aameen.

976
01:48:17.254 --> 01:48:19.613
-Aameen.
-Aameen.

977
01:48:19.854 --> 01:48:23.093
Give the Quran.

978
01:48:38.534 --> 01:48:45.693
Do not stray from the justice of the Quran.
do not deviate from its path. my son.

979
01:48:45.934 --> 01:48:49.173
Beat the drums

980
01:48:51.734 --> 01:48:56.653
Let the drums be
heard on the battlefield!

981
01:48:56.734 --> 01:49:02.213
Let the voices of the Alps
echo saying "Allah Allah."

982
01:49:02.254 --> 01:49:05.613
-Aameen.
-Aameen.

983
