option other than war.

1226
02:18:14.890 --> 02:18:19.929
Orhan Bey... Why are you
telling these tales to us?

1227
02:18:20.130 --> 02:18:23.609
For me. friendship
is really important.

1228
02:18:24.130 --> 02:18:27.249
That's why I came here.

1229
02:18:27.770 --> 02:18:29.249
And now I've made a decision.

1230
02:18:29.730 --> 02:18:34.009
Now you are my friend.

1231
02:18:35.570 --> 02:18:38.009
Have you made that
decision on your own?

1232
02:18:38.250 --> 02:18:40.009
Although it is my friendship?

1233
02:18:40.330 --> 02:18:44.649
I can choose both my friends and my enemies
on my own. I haven't seen any harm in it.

1234
02:18:46.010 --> 02:18:48.929
You didn't come all this
way for nothing. did you?

1235
02:18:49.770 --> 02:18:52.529
I want to hear your offer.

1236
02:18:52.850 --> 02:18:58.049
I hear you are preparing to
help Bursa. Bursa will fall soon.

1237
02:18:58.970 --> 02:19:02.969
What does that mean? How?

1238
02:19:03.250 --> 02:19:06.409
Silence!

1239
02:19:06.450 --> 02:19:08.569
Silence!

1240
02:19:08.730 --> 02:19:12.849
You will not interfere in this
matter. no soldiers no supplies.

1241
02:19:13.010 --> 02:19:16.809
Otherwise. as Bursa
falls it will fall upon Iznik.

1242
02:19:18.570 --> 02:19:23.769
I guess you haven't noticed the
walls surrounding Iznik. Orhan Bey.

1243
02:19:24.010 --> 02:19:27.089
They will never let anyone pass.

1244
02:19:27.170 --> 02:19:30.329
The moment you step outside
the gate. we will be everywhere.

1245
02:19:30.450 --> 02:19:33.729
You cannot leave or trade.
nothing will be possible for you.

1246
02:19:33.770 --> 02:19:36.009
I say you stay out
of the Bursa issue...

1247
02:19:36.050 --> 02:19:38.009
and I will open
the ways for you.

1248
02:19:38.050 --> 02:19:39.929
Trade freely.

1249
02:19:40.010 --> 02:19:43.129
Live freely in your city.

1250
02:19:43.170 --> 02:19:48.369
Do not condemn your people
to hunger and poverty like Bursa.

1251
02:19:49.610 --> 02:19:57.329
You speak as if Bursa is yours and you can
take Iznik whenever you want. Orhan Bey.

1252
02:19:58.170 --> 02:20:02.329
People of Iznik. I came here
to extend a hand of friendship.

1253
02:20:02.530 --> 02:20:06.249
You are all my witnesses. I ask
once more In front of all of you.

1254
02:20:06.530 --> 02:20:11.209
Will help go to Bursa or not?

1255
02:20:30.170 --> 02:20:32.449
Half of Iznik can be
bought with this gold.

1256
02:20:32.570 --> 02:20:35.129
Allah we can buy the
whole Iznik with this gold...

1257
02:20:35.330 --> 02:20:37.129
but we need to
think. of course.

1258
02:20:37.170 --> 02:20:41.769
You should not think. Dumrul. Your walnut sized
brain is not very good at thinking.

1259
02:20:43.810 --> 02:20:46.369
Look...

1260
02:20:56.610 --> 02:21:01.689
What happened? Aren't you
strong enough. you skinny man?

1261
02:21:03.290 --> 02:21:06.169
The backs of the Byzantine
infidels must be strong.

1262
02:21:06.210 --> 02:21:08.729
How did they load this
much gold onto this cart?

1263
02:21:08.850 --> 02:21:14.409
All those you called strong are
now lying on the ground. Balaban.

1264
02:21:14.650 --> 02:21:17.609
-You are right. -Come here.

1265
02:21:17.770 --> 02:21:20.009
Look at me!

1266
02:21:20.170 --> 02:21:23.489
If you ever insult me
again. I will beat you badly.

1267
02:21:24.130 --> 02:21:26.449
We should not waste
our time on the road.

1268
02:21:26.530 --> 02:21:29.089
Let's get ready.
Dumrul! Balaban!

1269
02:21:29.370 --> 02:21:33.049
You go to Orhan Bey and
give him the good news.

1270
02:21:33.370 --> 02:21:37.289
-You.
-We are not going to wander around with this gold.

1271
02:21:38.490 --> 02:21:41.689
We will do as Orhan Bey told us.

1272
02:21:50.050 --> 02:21:54.129
Byzantium will never
bow down to Turks.

1273
02:21:54.330 --> 02:21:57.289
Byzantium will bring your end.

1274
02:21:57.730 --> 02:22:01.729
Many Commanders who stood against
us are now buried under the ground.

1275
02:22:01.890 --> 02:22:03.609
Many castles fell.

1276
02:22:03.810 --> 02:22:07.369
Many mothers. many
lovers. many warriors suffered.

1277
02:22:08.330 --> 02:22:11.249
Bursa is still there.

1278
02:22:11.490 --> 02:22:14.089
I am a patient man. Lord.

1279
02:22:14.250 --> 02:22:17.929
Never You don t know what
is going to happen to you!

1280
02:22:18.130 --> 02:22:22.609
I don t know what i1s going to
happen to me. But Iznik will fall on you.

1281
02:22:24.130 --> 02:22:27.129
This conversation is over!

1282
02:22:27.930 --> 02:22:32.929
Nothing is over until I say so!

1283
02:22:40.970 --> 02:22:42.929
Listen to me carefully.

1284
02:22:43.090 --> 02:22:45.969
I extended my hand
to you. but you refused.

1285
02:22:46.050 --> 02:22:49.649
Everyone here witnessed it.
So do not blame me for anything!

1286
02:22:49.770 --> 02:22:51.649
When that day comes...

1287
02:22:51.770 --> 02:22:54.369
I will give everything
you have to your people!

1288
02:22:54.570 --> 02:22:56.729
I will free all of them!

1289
02:22:56.890 --> 02:23:02.249
People of Iznik! Whoever takes refug in my
land. their lives and goods will not be touched!

1290
02:23:02.530 --> 02:23:07.169
Whoever takes refuge under my
sanjak will practice their religion freely!

1291
02:23:07.290 --> 02:23:09.809
Whoever entrusts
his life to me...

1292
02:23:09.890 --> 02:23:12.249
will be protected
by me forever!

1293
02:23:12.490 --> 02:23:13.609
But...

1294
02:23:14.690 --> 02:23:17.569
whoever stands by him...

1295
02:23:18.130 --> 02:23:20.809
will be among
the ones who lose.

1296
02:23:27.250 --> 02:23:28.609
Safely.
